<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="w-full min-h-screen bg-zinc-900 text-white p-10">
        <p class="text-4xl mb-10">Hello Again! Log in to your account to dive back into the amazing world of <span class="text-yellow-500 text-5xl">PostHub</span>. Continue where you left off and engage with our vibrant community by sharing your stories and exploring new content. We've missed you!</p>
        <h3 class="text-3xl mb-5">Login Your Account</h3>
        <form action="/login" method="post">
            <input class="px-3 py-2 outline-none rounded-md bg-transparent border-2 border-zinc-800" type="email" name="email" placeholder="email">
            <input class="px-3 py-2 outline-none rounded-md bg-transparent border-2 border-zinc-800" type="password" name="password" placeholder="password">
            <input class="px-3 py-2 bg-yellow-500 rounded-md" type="submit" value="Login">
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>